{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-16",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_16_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Third Murder",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 5,
  "page_start_sec": 276.96,
  "page_end_sec": 519.54,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.545,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 276.96,
      "end": 277.42,
      "text": "She said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 277.62,
      "end": 280.28,
      "text": "\"If you don't go down there this very minute,"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.48,
      "end": 280.86,
      "text": "Sam,"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.0,
      "end": 281.856,
      "text": "I will and"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.06,
      "end": 283.4,
      "text": "I'll take the police down there.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 283.66,
      "end": 285.16,
      "text": "Her voice trembled,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.22,
      "end": 285.58,
      "text": "broke,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.78,
      "end": 287.0,
      "text": "and was thin and wailing."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.3,
      "end": 287.98,
      "text": "\"Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.0,
      "end": 288.36,
      "text": "Sam,"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.5,
      "end": 288.8,
      "text": "go!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 289.69,
      "end": 291.34,
      "text": "He stood up cursing her.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 291.5,
      "end": 292.34,
      "text": "Then he said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.5,
      "end": 293.2,
      "text": "\"Christ!"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.59,
      "end": 296.1,
      "text": "It'll be easier on my head than sitting here"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.18,
      "end": 297.36,
      "text": "listening to you squawk.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 298.14,
      "end": 299.08,
      "text": "He looked at his watch."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.94,
      "end": 301.6,
      "text": "\"You might as well lock up and go home.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 302.58,
      "end": 303.02,
      "text": "She said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 303.24,
      "end": 304.12,
      "text": "\"I won't."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.22,
      "end": 306.54,
      "text": "I'm going to wait right here till you come back.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 306.82,
      "end": 307.72,
      "text": "He said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 307.9,
      "end": 309.32,
      "text": "\"Do as you damned please,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 309.62,
      "end": 309.72,
      "text": "Put"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.048,
      "end": 310.72,
      "text": "his hat on,"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.82,
      "end": 311.54,
      "text": "flinched,"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.82,
      "end": 312.44,
      "text": "took it off,"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.78,
      "end": 314.86,
      "text": "and went out carrying it in his hand."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.64,
      "end": 316.6,
      "text": "An hour and a half later,"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.66,
      "end": 317.92,
      "text": "at 20 minutes past five,"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.0,
      "end": 318.54,
      "text": "Spade returned."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.34,
      "end": 320.04,
      "text": "He was cheerful."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.32,
      "end": 321.84,
      "text": "He came in asking,"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.52,
      "end": 323.3,
      "text": "what makes you so"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.46,
      "end": 324.48,
      "text": "hard to get along with,"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.56,
      "end": 324.82,
      "text": "sweetheart?"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.2,
      "end": 325.3,
      "text": "Me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.36,
      "end": 327.5,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.54,
      "end": 327.82,
      "text": "you."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.34,
      "end": 331.08,
      "text": "He put a finger on the tip of Effie Perrine's nose"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.3,
      "end": 332.06,
      "text": "and flattened it."
    },
    {
      "start": 332.26,
      "end": 334.24,
      "text": "He put his hands under her elbows,"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.42,
      "end": 335.52,
      "text": "lifted her straight up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.54,
      "end": 336.06,
      "text": "and kissed her"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.06,
      "end": 336.22,
      "text": "chin."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.16,
      "end": 339.0,
      "text": "He set her down on the floor again and asked:"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.52,
      "end": 341.12,
      "text": "\"Anything doing while I was gone?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 341.86,
      "end": 342.36,
      "text": "\"Luke—",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 343.104,
      "end": 343.76,
      "text": "what's his name?—"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.82,
      "end": 344.41,
      "text": "at the Belvedere"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.6,
      "end": 346.86,
      "text": "called up to tell you Cairo has returned."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.66,
      "end": 348.34,
      "text": "That was about half"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.34,
      "end": 348.96,
      "text": "an hour ago."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.08,
      "end": 351.32,
      "text": "Spade snapped his mouth shut,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 351.44,
      "end": 352.74,
      "text": "turned with a long step,"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.84,
      "end": 353.82,
      "text": "and started for the door."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.64,
      "end": 355.4,
      "text": "\"Did you find her?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 355.78,
      "end": 356.5,
      "text": "the girl called."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.5,
      "end": 358.74,
      "text": "\"Tell you about it when I'm back,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 359.04,
      "end": 360.42,
      "text": "he replied without pausing and"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.52,
      "end": 360.92,
      "text": "hurried out."
    },
    {
      "start": 361.98,
      "end": 363.96,
      "text": "A taxicab brought Spade to the Belvedere",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 363.96,
      "end": 365.4,
      "text": "within ten minutes of his departure"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.62,
      "end": 366.22,
      "text": "from his office."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.02,
      "end": 368.08,
      "text": "He found Luke in the lobby."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.44,
      "end": 371.38,
      "text": "The hotel-detective came grinning and shaking his head"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.38,
      "end": 372.14,
      "text": "to meet Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 372.96,
      "end": 373.72,
      "text": "\"Fifteen minutes late,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 373.82,
      "end": 374.22,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 374.66,
      "end": 375.92,
      "text": "\"Your bird has fluttered.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 376.576,
      "end": 377.64,
      "text": "Spade cursed his luck.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 378.688,
      "end": 379.04,
      "text": "\"Checked out—",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 379.16,
      "end": 379.52,
      "text": "gone"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.66,
      "end": 380.42,
      "text": "bag and baggage,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 380.62,
      "end": 381.04,
      "text": "Luke said."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.53,
      "end": 384.62,
      "text": "He took a battered memorandum-book from a vest-pocket,"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.12,
      "end": 385.76,
      "text": "licked his thumb,"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.82,
      "end": 386.56,
      "text": "thumbed pages,"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.84,
      "end": 388.82,
      "text": "and held the book out open to Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.632,
      "end": 391.62,
      "text": "\"There's the number of the taxi that hauled him."
    },
    {
      "start": 391.96,
      "end": 393.32,
      "text": "I got that much for you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 394.28,
      "end": 394.7,
      "text": "\"Thanks.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 395.68,
      "end": 397.76,
      "text": "Spade copied the number on the back of an envelope."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.48,
      "end": 399.44,
      "text": "\"Any forwarding address?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 400.22,
      "end": 400.72,
      "text": "\"No.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 401.82,
      "end": 403.78,
      "text": "He just come in carrying a big suitcase"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.22,
      "end": 407.24,
      "text": "and went upstairs and packed and come down with his stuff"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.44,
      "end": 409.62,
      "text": "and paid his bill and got a taxi"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.86,
      "end": 413.92,
      "text": "and went without anybody being able to hear what he told the driver."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.8,
      "end": 415.56,
      "text": "\"How about his trunk?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 416.64,
      "end": 417.86,
      "text": "Luke's lower lip sagged.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 417.98,
      "end": 418.68,
      "text": "\"By God,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 418.88,
      "end": 419.22,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.3,
      "end": 420.06,
      "text": "\"I forgot that!"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.22,
      "end": 420.66,
      "text": "Come on.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 421.06,
      "end": 422.74,
      "text": "They went up to Cairo's room.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 422.9,
      "end": 423.86,
      "text": "The trunk was there."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.42,
      "end": 425.76,
      "text": "It was closed, but not locked."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.0,
      "end": 427.16,
      "text": "They raised the lid."
    },
    {
      "start": 427.34,
      "end": 428.52,
      "text": "The trunk was empty."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.44,
      "end": 429.8,
      "text": "Luke said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.46,
      "end": 431.68,
      "text": "\"What do you know about that!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 432.672,
      "end": 433.78,
      "text": "Spade did not say anything.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 434.49,
      "end": 436.08,
      "text": "Spade went back to his office.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 436.736,
      "end": 438.59,
      "text": "Effie Perine looked up at him, inquisitively."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.98,
      "end": 440.2,
      "text": "\"Missed him,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 440.34,
      "end": 442.22,
      "text": "Spade grumbled and passed into his"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.36,
      "end": 442.82,
      "text": "private room."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.56,
      "end": 444.38,
      "text": "She followed him in."
    },
    {
      "start": 444.97,
      "end": 447.28,
      "text": "He sat in his chair and began to roll a cigarette."
    },
    {
      "start": 447.98,
      "end": 448.6,
      "text": "She sat on"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.6,
      "end": 450.2,
      "text": "the desk in front of him and put her"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.2,
      "end": 452.02,
      "text": "toes on a corner of his chair-seat."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.98,
      "end": 454.09,
      "text": "\"What about Miss O'Shaughnessy?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 454.34,
      "end": 454.82,
      "text": "she demanded."
    },
    {
      "start": 455.18,
      "end": 456.4,
      "text": "\"I missed her too,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 456.54,
      "end": 457.0,
      "text": "he replied,"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.28,
      "end": 458.56,
      "text": "but she had been there."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.22,
      "end": 459.95,
      "text": "\"On the _La Paloma_?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 460.36,
      "end": 461.54,
      "text": "\"_The La_ is",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 461.54,
      "end": 462.34,
      "text": "a lousy combination,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 462.7,
      "end": 463.12,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.4,
      "end": 464.42,
      "text": "Stop it."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.48,
      "end": 465.12,
      "text": "Be nice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.24,
      "end": 465.42,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.6,
      "end": 466.02,
      "text": "Tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.08,
      "end": 468.34,
      "text": "He set fire to his cigarette,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 468.52,
      "end": 469.0,
      "text": "pocketed"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.12,
      "end": 469.52,
      "text": "his lighter,"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.66,
      "end": 470.6,
      "text": "patted her shins,"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.6,
      "end": 471.0,
      "text": "and said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.14,
      "end": 471.64,
      "text": "\"Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.04,
      "end": 472.64,
      "text": "_La Paloma_."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.12,
      "end": 474.94,
      "text": "She got down there at a little after noon"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.12,
      "end": 475.46,
      "text": "yesterday."
    },
    {
      "start": 475.84,
      "end": 477.18,
      "text": "He pulled his brows down."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.94,
      "end": 480.5,
      "text": "That means she went straight there after leaving the cab"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.7,
      "end": 481.6,
      "text": "at the ferry building."
    },
    {
      "start": 482.36,
      "end": 483.46,
      "text": "It's only a few piers away."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.02,
      "end": 485.24,
      "text": "The Captain wasn't aboard."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.62,
      "end": 486.84,
      "text": "His name's Jacobi"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.0,
      "end": 488.44,
      "text": "and she asked for him by name."
    },
    {
      "start": 488.74,
      "end": 490.38,
      "text": "He was uptown on business."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.4,
      "end": 493.06,
      "text": "That would mean he didn't expect her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.38,
      "end": 494.26,
      "text": "or not at that time"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.28,
      "end": 494.6,
      "text": "anyway."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.52,
      "end": 497.6,
      "text": "She waited there till he came back at four o'clock."
    },
    {
      "start": 498.0,
      "end": 501.16,
      "text": "They spent the time from then till meal-time in his cabin"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.22,
      "end": 502.18,
      "text": "and she ate with him.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 503.36,
      "end": 504.86,
      "text": "He inhaled and exhaled smoke,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 505.58,
      "end": 508.82,
      "text": "turned his head aside to spit a yellow tobacco-flake off his lip,"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.84,
      "end": 509.38,
      "text": "and went on:"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.432,
      "end": 511.04,
      "text": "\"After the meal"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.1,
      "end": 513.06,
      "text": "Captain Jacobi had three more visitors."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.76,
      "end": 514.66,
      "text": "One of them was Gutman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.82,
      "end": 516.05,
      "text": "and one was Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.56,
      "end": 519.54,
      "text": "and one was the kid who delivered Gutman's message to you yesterday."
    }
  ],
  "corrected": "claude"
}